Defendant Linda A Korth in court with attorney Samuel W. Benedict.  David John Behm appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  The State moves to amend to a county ordinance of retail theft.  The Court amends the charge accordingly, enters a no contest plea and finds the Defendant guilty.    The Defendant was sentenced as follows:

Count #1:

FINE: $267.50 (to be paid at  $25.00 per month commencing 11/16/16 or serve 6 days jail, consecutive, as penalty for non payment of fine);
